ZH: 我今天买了一支新钢笔。
EN: I bought a new fountain pen today.

ZH: 我的钢笔是黑色的。
EN: My pen is black.

ZH: 这支钢笔写起来很顺畅。
EN: This pen writes very smoothly.

ZH: 我喜欢用钢笔写字。
EN: I like writing with a fountain pen.

ZH: 我的钢笔坏了，需要修理。
EN: My fountain pen is broken and needs to be repaired.

ZH: 这支钢笔的价格很贵。
EN: The price of this pen is very expensive.

ZH: 这支钢笔的墨水颜色很美。
EN: The ink color of this pen is very pretty.

ZH: 我常常忘记带钢笔。
EN: I often forget to bring my fountain pen.

ZH: 我的钢笔用完了，需要换墨水。
EN: My pen has run out of ink and needs a refill.

ZH: 钢笔的笔杆非常精致。
EN: The body of the fountain pen is very delicate.

ZH: 这支钢笔是我最喜欢的。
EN: This pen is my favorite.

ZH: 这支钢笔是礼物，我很喜欢。
EN: This pen is a gift, I like it very much.

ZH: 我的钢笔签字很漂亮。
EN: My fountain pen has a beautiful signature.

ZH: 钢笔的墨水是蓝色的。
EN: The ink of the fountain pen is blue.

ZH: 我的爷爷留给我的钢笔很珍贵。
EN: The fountain pen my grandfather left me is very precious.

ZH: 我每天用钢笔写日记。
EN: I use a fountain pen to write a diary every day.

ZH: 我的钢笔在包里找不到了。
EN: My fountain pen is missing in my bag.

ZH: 钢笔的笔尖很尖。
EN: The tip of the fountain pen is very sharp.

ZH: 我的钢笔是纪念品。
EN: My pen is a souvenir.

ZH: 这支钢笔是限量版。
EN: This fountain pen is a limited edition.
